flowchart TD
    Start([Import Configuration Request]) --> PM[ConfigurationImportManager]
    PM --> CreateContext[Create OrchestrationContext]
    CreateContext --> StoreRequest[Store ImportRequest in Context]
    StoreRequest --> InitStats[Initialize ImportStatistics]
    
    InitStats --> Step1[ValidateRequestStep]
    Step1 --> V1{Valid Request?}
    V1 -->|No| ErrorV1[Return: Invalid request]
    V1 -->|Yes| Step2[TruncateDataStep]
    
    Step2 --> V2{Clear Existing Data?}
    V2 -->|No| Step3[InitializeDatabaseStep]
    V2 -->|Yes| Truncate[Execute: Clear existing sequences, resources, parameters]
    Truncate --> TruncateComplete[Update Statistics: Records cleared]
    TruncateComplete --> Step3
    
    Step3 --> DBInit[Execute: EnsureCreated, Apply Migrations]
    DBInit --> DBComplete[Update Context: Database ready]
    DBComplete --> Step4[GetConfigurationStep]
    
    Step4 --> GW1[GrpcGateway.ExecuteAsync]
    GW1 --> CreateOp[ExecutionConfigurationOperations.CreateGetCurrentConfigurationOperation]
    CreateOp --> GrpcReq[new FetchExecutionConfigurationRequest]
    GrpcReq --> ExecuteGrpc[Execute gRPC call with retry]
    
    ExecuteGrpc --> GrpcResult{Success?}
    GrpcResult -->|No| ErrorGrpc[Return: gRPC call failed]
    GrpcResult -->|Yes| StoreConfig[Store Configuration in Context]
    StoreConfig --> StoreReqId[Store RequestId in Context]
    
    StoreReqId --> Step5[ImportSequencesStep]
    Step5 --> ProcessSeq[Process each sequence from configuration]
    ProcessSeq --> SeqLoop{More sequences?}
    SeqLoop -->|Yes| CreateSeq[Create Sequence entity]
    CreateSeq --> ProcessParams[Process sequence parameters]
    ProcessParams --> SaveSeq[Save to database]
    SaveSeq --> UpdateSeqStats[Update Statistics: Sequences imported]
    UpdateSeqStats --> SeqLoop
    
    SeqLoop -->|No| Step6[ImportResourcesStep]
    Step6 --> ProcessRes[Process each resource from configuration]
    ProcessRes --> ResLoop{More resources?}
    ResLoop -->|Yes| CreateRes[Create Resource entity]
    CreateRes --> SaveRes[Save to database]
    SaveRes --> UpdateResStats[Update Statistics: Resources imported]
    UpdateResStats --> ResLoop
    
    ResLoop -->|No| FinalCheck[Check for accumulated errors]
    FinalCheck --> HasErrors{Any errors?}
    HasErrors -->|Yes| PartialSuccess[Set IsSuccess = false with partial completion]
    HasErrors -->|No| FullSuccess[Set IsSuccess = true]
    
    PartialSuccess --> ExtractResults[Extract results from context]
    FullSuccess --> ExtractResults
    
    ExtractResults --> BuildResult[Build ConfigurationImportResult]
    BuildResult --> SetDuration[Set total duration]
    SetDuration --> SetSteps[Set completed steps list]
    SetSteps --> SetStats[Set final statistics]
    SetStats --> Return([Return ConfigurationImportResult])
    
    %% Error paths
    ErrorV1 --> Return
    ErrorGrpc --> Return
    
    %% Styling
    classDef stepClass fill:#00bfff,stroke:#2d2d2d
    classDef gatewayClass fill:#46c246,stroke:#f57c00
    classDef errorClass fill:#ffebee,stroke:#d32f2f
    classDef successClass fill:#e8f5e8,stroke:#388e3c
    classDef contextClass fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2
    
    class Step1,Step2,Step3,Step4,Step5,Step6 stepClass
    class GW1,CreateOp,GrpcReq,ExecuteGrpc gatewayClass
    class ErrorV1,ErrorGrpc errorClass
    class FullSuccess,PartialSuccess successClass
    class CTX1,CTX2,CTX3,CTX4,CTX5,CTX6 contextClass
    
    %% Notes
    note1[Note: Each step can fail independently<br/>and choose whether to continue]
    note2[Note: Statistics track:<br/>- Sequences imported<br/>- Resources imported<br/>- Parameters processed<br/>- Errors encountered]
    note3[Note: GrpcGateway provides:<br/>- Automatic retries<br/>- Timeout handling<br/>- Concurrency control<br/>- Statistics tracking]